snippet.textDisplay:
The music production, the detailed instrumentation, the fusion of Hindustani Classical + Western Classical + Contemporary portions is just so effortless. From 7:00 especially the crescendo of Hina's voice and Amanat Ali's versatility just takes my breath away. Coke Studio Pakistan continues to reach new heights in music and introducing us to such stunning classical music. Love from India!

Happy Independence Day to everybody! :)
